     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA05d122n2-ptr" id="PJA05d122n2">2</a>
      <p>Possibly Ward means the army, or he may be referring to the navys commodore, Esek Hopkins.</p>
     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA05d122n3-ptr" id="PJA05d122n3">3</a>
